The paper discusses the use of deep learning for image correction in mobile-phone-based microscopes, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions the use of denoising techniques, which could be categorized under information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM). The use of deep learning for image correction is also a form of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
